data.title: CAT ON THE CHAIR , INSPIRED BY AMEDEO CLEMENTE MODIGLIANI 65 x 80 x 2 cm
data.meta_description:
Version of famous portrait of Woman on the chair  with a cat inspired by Modigliani Masterpieces .
I have done one of them for cats lovers in oil on canvas .
Signed on the front
I created this painting using fine artist oil paints which will not fade when they get exposed to UV light Painting continues around the edges of the deep wooden box canvas giving a very contemporary style although it can be framed if you wish
This work is sold unframed and shipped in cardboard box which is very secure for shipping canvases
